sources.title: Northern Frontier (1935) KERMIT MAYNARDüçï COWBOY WESTERN
sources.description:
Stars: Kermit Maynard, Fred Kohler, Paul Hurst
Director: Forrest Sheldon

 A Canadian Mountie tracks and captures the murderers of a fur trapper but is later overpowered, tied to a tree, and left in the woods to die. The Mountie's brother finds him just before he dies and sets out to recapture the killers.

metadata.Plot: The Mounties are after counterfeiters. When McKenzie catches an arriving agent, he uses that man's letter of introduction to get into the counterfeiting gang. Greatly outnumbered and in trouble when his true identity becomes known, he receives unexpected help from one of the gang members.
metadata.Actors: Kermit Maynard, Eleanor Hunt, Russell Hopton
